description: Proudly offering the pinnacle of luxury living in this extraordinary, one-of-a-kind brownstone on the highly sought after East Side of South Boston. Spanning three impeccably designed floors, this ARCHITECTURAL GEM seamlessly fuses timeless historic character with cutting-edge modern sophistication. No detail has been overlooked—from the exquisite CUSTOM MILLWORK to the flawless DESIGNER FINISHES throughout. With a show-stopping, STATE-OF-THE ART kitchen equipped with dual oversized islands, ideal for grand entertaining and the entire second floor dedicated to a lavish primary suite, this brownstone offers unmatched privacy, comfort, and sophistication. The convenience of a private, two-car HEATED garage and a fully Crestron-integrated smart home system further elevates this home's prestige. With the potential to transform the rooftop into a breathtaking urban oasis, this residence offers a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to own an ICONIC piece of Boston real estate.
